title: Love Actually
overview: Do opposites really attract? An Qing Huan is a career woman who is highly driven to succeed. She is focused on her career and works very hard to work toward her goals in life. Ding Ren Jian is an IT engineer who doesn't think much past what he needs to do on a daily basis. He lives in the moment and tries to deal with what life throws at him. When Qing Huan meets Ren Jian, the two can't seem more different from each other. But as they both deal with their bustling lives, will they realize that they have more in common than they thought?
